                            the first was shut away in a room and the children in the second group,
                            consisting of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/3598">eighteen boys and twelve girls</persName>, were initiated into the
                            clerical state by being tonsured. </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/ordination"/>
                    </event>
                </listEvent>
                <bibl type="primary">
